channel.title: -Webclient Freezes At L.G.E, Autocache Downloader Added-
channel.description:
So i jar and signed my client. Everything (client.jar) works fine on my desktop, starts downloading cache.. runs fine. When i uploaded it to my host it starts the java, than gets stuck on the client: Loading Game Engine.
Just sits there, if i go away from the page it goes white. I had a webclient working fine but over 60+ players i'd say quit because they couldn't download or didn't like too.
Can somebody please help me on this error?
[img]http://www.elitedemons.org/images/uploads/Web_Error.png[/img]
